&gt;先租後買，係畀人換樓用。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有人無錢買樓，又無力借錢上會，橫掂租樓，每月畀多少少，可以坐往去睇市，個市升，就上東張話自己眼光好。個市跌，就扮儍，話律師面對面同佢講係死約，佢又即場問經紀，經紀話唔使驚，無嘢嘅。。。佢唔信律師而信經紀，而即場律師又唔同佢講“喂，點會無嘢？係死約喎”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;結果，一年後，個市跌到七個一皮，當然唔想用原價“先租後買”，即刻出去買平貨。。。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;未知會出事，會打畀經紀仲錄音？奇！小心得來好漂忽。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;出事就揾東張？點解唔揾律師？還是律師叫佢“不如試吓東張啦，我就無乜計。”&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32023017&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=207131390468b7c426159485_67871577"/><published>2025-09-03T01:02:02+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f673e691de64872a50d5193c236b6ce7</id><title>「先租後買」不及「光豬買賣」明確</title><updated>2025-09-03T01:29:16+08:00</updated><author><name>阿柒回歸</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-03T01:29:16+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573835183"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573835183"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ekSJZ2kVL5E?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/ekSJZ2kVL5E?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/ekSJZ2kVL5E?feature=shared&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32023021&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=207131390468b7c426159485_67